data.description: Start your day drinking coffee on the covered front porch or relax in the evening watching the sunset go down.  Enter the house with an open flowing floor plan, large dining room with bay windows for plenty of light. Spacious living room with double doors leading into a large back yard with multiple trees and one producing fig tree. The kitchen is fully equipped with refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, and gas stove and oven which conveys with sale. The laundry room is off the kitchen with extra shelving and plenty of room for more built ins.  The three bedrooms are large so you won't feel cramped. New roof installed 05-26-2023. This house is located within .5 miles of three city parks, a block from the elementary school and is in walking distance to Main St.  Enjoy the small town living with quick access to Hwy 82. Within 30 miles of casino, lakes, and bigger cities for shopping and entertainment.  This could be the place you call HOME! Call me or your favorite agent for a showing.
